msgstr ""
"你可以通过内置函数 :func:`next` 执行生成器到下一个 ``yield``。换句话说，生成"
"器运行，然后暂停。例如："

#: ../../howto/a-conceptual-overview-of-asyncio.rst:157
msgid ""
">>> generator = get_random_number()\n"
">>> next(generator)\n"
"Hi\n"
"1\n"
">>> next(generator)\n"
"Hello\n"
"7"
msgstr ""
">>> generator = get_random_number()\n"
">>> next(generator)\n"
